    "chapter": {
        "bookTitle": "1 Thessalonians",
        "delineation": "Chapter",
        "number": 5,
        "summary": "The Saints will know the season of the Second Coming of Christ\u2014Live the way Saints should live\u2014Rejoice evermore\u2014Do not despise prophesyings.",
        "chapterAugmentations": [],
        "verses": [
            {
                "text": "But of the times and the seasons, brethren, ye have no need that I write unto you.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For yourselves know perfectly that the day of the Lord so cometh as a thief in the night.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Day of the Lord; Millennium, Preparing a People for.",
                        "start": 39,
                        "end": 42
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 106:4.",
                        "start": 70,
                        "end": 75
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For when they shall say, Peace and safety; then sudden destruction cometh upon them, as travail upon a woman with child; and they shall not escape.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Refuge.",
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 41
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "D&C 1:2.",
                        "start": 140,
                        "end": 146
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But ye, brethren, are not in darkness, that that day should overtake you as a thief.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Rom. 13:12 (12\u201313).",
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 37
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Luke 17:24; 21:34.",
                        "start": 49,
                        "end": 52
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Ye are all the children of light, and the children of the day: we are not of the night, nor of darkness.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0sons. TG\u00a0Children of Light.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 23
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Therefore let us not sleep, as do others; but let us watch and be sober.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Sleep.",
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 26
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Watch.",
                        "start": 53,
                        "end": 58
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0sober, vigilant, circumspect. TG\u00a0Abstain.",
                        "start": 66,
                        "end": 71
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 31,
                        "end": 33
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "For they that sleep sleep in the night; and they that be drunken are drunken in the night.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "But let us, who are of the day, be sober, putting on the breastplate of faith and love; and for an helmet, the hope of salvation.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Levity.",
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 40
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Rom. 13:12; Eph. 6:11 (11\u201318).",
                        "start": 57,
                        "end": 68
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Col. 1:4 (4\u20135); 1\u00a0Thes. 1:3.",
                        "start": 72,
                        "end": 77
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Hope.",
                        "start": 111,
                        "end": 115
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "For God hath not appointed us to wrath, but to obtain salvation by our Lord Jesus Christ,",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "1\u00a0Thes. 1:10; 1\u00a0Pet. 2:8 (6\u20138).",
                        "start": 33,
                        "end": 38
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Salvation.",
                        "start": 54,
                        "end": 63
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Who died for us, that, whether we wake or sleep, we should live together with him.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Immortality.",
                        "start": 59,
                        "end": 63
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Wherefore comfort yourselves together, and edify one another, even as also ye do.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0exhort, console, encourage.",
                        "start": 10,
                        "end": 17
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Edification.",
                        "start": 43,
                        "end": 48
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And we beseech you, brethren, to know them which labour among you, and are over you in the Lord, and admonish you;",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Leadership.",
                        "start": 49,
                        "end": 55
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And to esteem them very highly in love for their work's sake. And be at peace among yourselves.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "Philip. 2:29. TG\u00a0Respect.",
                        "start": 7,
                        "end": 13
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "Mark 9:50; Rom. 15:5 (1\u20137); D&C 20:54 (53\u201355).",
                        "start": 72,
                        "end": 77
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 62,
                        "end": 65
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Now we exhort you, brethren, warn them that are unruly, comfort the feebleminded, support the weak, be patient toward all men.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Warn.",
                        "start": 29,
                        "end": 33
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "2\u00a0Thes. 3:11.",
                        "start": 48,
                        "end": 54
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0encourage, console.",
                        "start": 56,
                        "end": 63
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0faint-hearted, despondent.",
                        "start": 68,
                        "end": 80
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0care for.",
                        "start": 82,
                        "end": 89
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0infirm, doubting, timid.",
                        "start": 94,
                        "end": 98
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 122,
                        "end": 126
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "See that none render evil for evil unto any man; but ever follow that which is good, both among yourselves, and to all men.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Retribution.",
                        "start": 14,
                        "end": 20
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Forbear.",
                        "start": 21,
                        "end": 25
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 44,
                        "end": 48
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 119,
                        "end": 123
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Rejoice evermore.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Joy.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 7
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Pray without ceasing.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Prayer.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 4
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "In every thing give thanks: for this is the will of God in Christ Jesus concerning you.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Communication; Thanksgiving.",
                        "start": 20,
                        "end": 26
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Quench not the Spirit.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0Extinguish, Hinder, Suppress.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 6
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Holy Ghost, Gifts of; Holy Ghost, Loss of.",
                        "start": 15,
                        "end": 21
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Despise not prophesyings.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Prove all things; hold fast that which is good.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0Examine, Put to the test. 1\u00a0Jn. 4:1 (1\u20136). TG\u00a0Study; Test.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 5
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Abstain from all appearance of evil.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Abstain.",
                        "start": 0,
                        "end": 7
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "GR\u00a0kinds. TG\u00a0Apparel.",
                        "start": 17,
                        "end": 27
                    },
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Evil.",
                        "start": 31,
                        "end": 35
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "And the very God of peace sanctify you wholly; and I pray God your whole spirit and soul and body be preserved blameless unto the coming of our Lord Jesus Christ.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "TG\u00a0Sanctification.",
                        "start": 26,
                        "end": 34
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 51,
                        "end": 61
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Faithful is he that calleth you, who also will do it.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 9,
                        "end": 11
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 50,
                        "end": 53
                    }
                ]
            },
            {
                "text": "Brethren, pray for us.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "Greet all the brethren with an holy kiss.",
                "footnotes": [
                    {
                        "footnote": "JST\u00a01\u00a0Thes. 5:26 \u2026 salutation.",
                        "start": 36,
                        "end": 40
                    }
                ],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "I charge you by the Lord that this epistle be read unto all the holy brethren.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": []
            },
            {
                "text": "The grace of our Lord Jesus Christ be with you. Amen.",
                "footnotes": [],
                "associatedContents": [],
                "italics": [
                    {
                        "start": 35,
                        "end": 37
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    }
}